01/02/2010
PODGORICA, Montenegro -- Police arrested on Saturday (January 30th) a Montenegrin citizen wanted by Italian authorities for allegedly belonging to an international group of drug smugglers moving cocaine to Italy via Colombia. 
The suspect was detained in the town of Bar on an Interpol warrant. 
Police are searching for three others in connection. 
(Vjesti, Beta, B92 - 31/01/10; RTCG - 30/01/10)
